body_html: Unless you've had bad luck with the particular commit you're at, all the tests should pass (see https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/README.md, build status at head is in there, or look at ci.tensorflow.org for details). The tensorflow-master-* builds are the ones you want to look at, unless you're using a release. All tests should pass in a release.
